\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8a09492619fa40c4c0118164dd2c22357c89b35","tid":2278514,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4db8d878e95ec00a158b6654ae0ccdec6dd31b1c","tid":2278514,"uid":100155,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"83df0deb4ec41b21db441f514b9cd6bd9cb9d5dc","tid":2278514,"uid":63909,"like":129,"dislike":2,"score":127,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T08:19:41.000Z","msg":"大量美國人真心無邏輯思維"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T09:02:57.000Z","msg":"吸毒濫交幻幻就好有品德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T10:50:36.000Z","msg":"性自主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e222abfb9a836e281af6eb89e852552618b3910c","tid":2278514,"uid":345502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e0517210149749daa5cde11cddb7160ef7dfbaa","tid":2278514,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T08:16:07.000Z","msg":"在拜登宣佈確定當選後，CNN 時事評論員范瓊斯（Van Jones）在節目上分析論述，講到激動處，突然哽咽，說：「身為父親，現在我鬆了一口氣，我終於可以告訴我的孩子：品行是重要的、是有意義的，誠實是重要的，做一個好人也是重要的。」<br />\n暗指過去川普的行徑，難以令人家長說服、教育小孩。這段畫面曝光後，吸引不少網友目光，更在社群網站上瘋傳。<br />\n如果只選一個能令家長教子女的人做總統，以後美國總統候選人最好由幼稚園教師此一組別初選。<br />\n政客和律師，都是好人？即將上任的這位總統，都具有這兩重身份。<br />\nCome on man, you can do better.<br />\n以這位主持人的標準：民主黨前總統克林頓與女助理萊溫斯基，動用雪茄做性侵犯的工具，在國會接受問話，繪聲繪色，請問克林頓是不是教好子女的好人典型？<br />\n川普的兒子最少沒有吸毒，川普的女兒貴氣，沒有紋身性濫交。<br />\n當左派仇恨川普，他們說：川普無法令我如何教好孩子。<br />\n但當拜登被揭發並沒有教好兒子，他們說：兒子作風即使敗壞，跟父親沒有關係。<br />\n在中國歷史上，曹操是好人還是壞人？曾國藩是好人還是壞人？蔣介石是好人還是壞人？<br />\n但這種名嘴，是沒有這種知識邏輯的。他們憑一句話，再在電視鏡頭前抹眼淚，就將許多頭腦簡單的人也跟着大愛感動，點頭說：對對對。<br />\n<br />\n陶傑<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/272574169481780/posts/4592983614107459/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F272574169481780%2Fposts%2F4592983614107459%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2BQESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=8e1bd387\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/272574169481780/posts/4592983614107459/?d=n</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T10:50:39.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，拜登d私德......."},{"pid":"b5ef83404f1ab63faa50e150d85f90d9b216e905","tid":2278514,"uid":273360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T10:50:53.000Z","msg":"即係平時無家教囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />國家元首品格同自己點培育下一代關閪事咩屌你老母"},{"pid":"791b1a88cb87fb6b1ed826e2c9e5b125841505b8","tid":2278514,"uid":138868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T10:51:07.000Z","msg":"希特拉做人夠唔夠完美？<br />\n愛國愛環保愛動物食齋早睡早起唔飲酒冇婚外情"},{"pid":"7763e9f6ac23321a4147f09ec9adf5c8d9e49bcd","tid":2278514,"uid":345502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0a609c1aeb2c3f83c1e0042b85e1c7cca2745aa","tid":2278514,"uid":32221,"like":80,"dislike":0,"score":80,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T08:22:14.000Z","msg":"漏左啲喎<br />\n雙重標準是重要的、偽善是重要的、更重要是為人民幣服務是要堅持的"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T10:51:13.000Z","msg":"仲有幼幼同亂倫....."},{"pid":"e7f9079d0199694aa3ffb42a49fc3d321e25c674","tid":2278514,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"83df0deb4ec41b21db441f514b9cd6bd9cb9d5dc","tid":2278514,"uid":63909,"like":129,"dislike":2,"score":127,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T08:19:41.000Z","msg":"大量美國人真心無邏輯思維"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T10:51:13.000Z","msg":"黑人嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9477aa8419794fe904a0cbea57afe5a322e8bb21","tid":2278514,"uid":271513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T10:51:26.000Z","msg":"譯做英文直線抽擊cnn la"},{"pid":"30454fdf10d83e7018343bfd507d35ef37b5075e","tid":2278514,"uid":345502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4fa0dccd4523c94b124cb43db85a825ec71334e5","tid":2278514,"uid":148315,"like":69,"dislike":0,"score":69,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T08:23:03.000Z","msg":"Trump一家個個端莊高貴<br />\n<br />\nBiden個仔叫雞吸毒貪污<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=